devdoc.details: A contract that demonstrates a simple loop to compute the sum of all numbers up to a specified maximum.

test(uint256).details: Computes the sum of all integers from 0 up to a specified maximum (exclusive). This function uses a `for` loop to iterate from 0 to `max - 1` and adds each value to a cumulative sum.

params.max: The upper limit (exclusive) for the summation.

returns._0: sum The sum of all integers from 0 up to `max`.
